{"title":"欢迎之歌","authors":["萧三"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":11,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢迎之歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"萧三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军跨上千里马"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前来访问新中华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六亿人民大高兴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"载歌载舞欢迎他"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军大名金日成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寰球到处都闻名"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他领导朝鲜人民军"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打败了万恶美国兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保住了江山三千里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扑灭了战火在远东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戳穿了美帝纸老虎"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝鲜人民立下一大功"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中朝自古称善邻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白山绿水长相亲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抗美援朝保家国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出现最可爱的人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"志愿军和人民军"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝鲜人和中国人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲亲密密无间隙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相处如同一家人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜血凝结友谊固"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万古常青同心曲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了和平归来日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难舍难分人尽哭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此景此情感人深"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寄语姐妹与弟兄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我你永远手携手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我你永远心连心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深情厚谊成诗篇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艺术壮丽得再现"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清歌妙舞迷人甚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“高地相逢”请细看（注）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢迎，欢迎金将军"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢迎，欢迎众贵宾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢迎你们骑上千里马"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢迎你们看看咱干劲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们和你们——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔赴一个共同的目的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们和你们——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在一个伟大的阵营"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纸老虎还在张牙又舞爪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要消灭共同的敌人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们深知"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们深信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国人——朝鲜人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千秋万代一条心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（注）“在高地相逢”是此次朝鲜艺术团演出的一个节目，表现朝鲜人民军和中国人民志愿军会合共同抗美情景。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}